---
layout: layouts/listing.njk
title: Quotes
description: Passages worth sitting with — from teachers, texts, and unexpected places.
navSection: quotes
---

<header class="page-header">
  <p class="page-header__eyebrow">Quotes</p>
  <h1 class="page-header__title">Passages worth sitting with</h1>
  <p class="page-header__subtitle">
    Lines that stopped me, or that keep returning.
  </p>
</header>

<p class="section-intro">
  Not annotations or arguments — just passages I find worth returning to,
  with a note on why they landed.
</p>

<ul class="entry-list">

  {% for item in collections.quotes %}
  <li class="entry-list__item">
    <div class="entry-list__body">
      <p class="entry-list__meta">{{ item.data.meta }}</p>
      <h3><a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a></h3>
      <p class="entry-list__excerpt">{{ item.data.excerpt }}</p>
    </div>
  </li>
  {% endfor %}

</ul>
